            <article>
                <h3>25/09/2025</h3>
                <p>We are pleased to announce that our article has been accepted in <em>The Journal of Physical Chemistry C</em>:</p>
                <p><strong>Delving into the correlation between magnetic and lattice degrees of freedom from magnetocaloric and magnetovolume effects in Lu<sub>2</sub>Fe<sub>17</sub> ribbons</strong></p>
                <p><em>Authors:</em> José Garrido-Álvarez, María Arreguín Hernández, Cristina Echevarría Bonet, Pedro Gorria, Inés Puente Orench, François Fauth, Jesús Blanco, José Luis Sánchez Llamazares, Pablo Álvarez-Alonso</p>
                <p><em>Manuscript ID:</em> jp-2025-04207h — <em>Status:</em> Accept</p>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>09/09/2025</h3>
                <p>Elif Cansu Aslantuğ, Erasmus master’s student from Adiyaman University (Turkey), visits us. She will work on the synthesis of low-temperature shape memory magnetic materials.</p>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>01/06/2025</h3>
