            <article>
                <h3>29/01/2025</h3>
                <p>We are pleased to announce that our students José Luis Garrido Álvarez and Alba Sanz Prada participate in 
                    <a href="https://gefes2025.com/" target="_blank">GEFES 2025</a> with two works:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>José Luis Garrido Álvarez: <strong>Magnetic Structure Investigation of the Ternary Rare-Earth-based Compound TbFeSi</strong></li>
                    <li>Alba Sanz Prada: <strong>Enhancement of the Thermoelectric Figure of Merit by Combination of Doping and Grain Boundary Engineering in ZrNi(Sn,Sb)</strong></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="image-gallery">
                    <figure class="image-item">
                        <img src="https://github.com/GrupoDeMagnetismo/MagCaloricH/blob/GrupoDeMagnetismo-Pictures/Alba-GEFES.jpg?raw=true" alt="Poster Alba Sanz Prada">
                        <figcaption>
                            <strong>Magnetic Structure Investigation of the Ternary Rare-Earth-based Compound TbFeSi</strong>
                        </figcaption>
                        <p>This poster presents a detailed study of the magnetic structure of the ternary rare-earth-based compound TbFeSi synthesized by rapid solidification.</p>
                    </figure>
                    <figure class="image-item">
                        <img src="https://github.com/GrupoDeMagnetismo/MagCaloricH/blob/GrupoDeMagnetismo-Pictures/Garrido-GEFES.jpg?raw=true" alt="Poster José Luis Garrido Álvarez">
                        <figcaption>
                            <strong>Enhancement of the Thermoelectric Figure of Merit by Combination of Doping and Grain Boundary Engineering in ZrNi(Sn,Sb)</strong>
                        </figcaption>
                        <p>This poster describes how the combination of doping and grain boundary engineering improves the thermoelectric figure of merit.</p>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </article>

