                <h3>13/11/2024</h3>
                <p>Visiting professors Horacio Flores Zúñiga and Juan Pablo Camarillo García presented their works on Caloric Effects in Heusler-type Alloys to the university community.</p>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>01/11/2024</h3>
                <p>Professors Horacio Flores Zúñiga from 
                <a href="https://ipicyt.edu.mx/curricular/HoracioFloresZ%C3%BA%C3%B1iga/tesis" target="_blank">IPICYT</a> and Juan Pablo Camarillo García 
                <a href="https://materiales.uaz.edu.mx/personalacademico/dr-juan-pablo-ramon-camarillo-garcia/" target="_blank">UAZ</a> (Mexico) visited us. We will work on the development of caloric effect materials.</p>
            </article>

